===Transitive Verb===
{{en-verb|babbl|ing}}

# To utter in an indistinct or incoherent way; to repeat, as words, in a childish way without understanding.
#:*These words he used to '''babble''' in all companies. - [[Arbuthnot]].
# To disclose by too free talk, as a secret.


